Study

PV (cluster resource) ↔ PVC (user request) — bound 1:1.
Access modes: RWO, ROX, RWX, RWOP.
Reclaim policy: Retain, Delete, Recycle (deprecated).
StorageClass → dynamic provisioning via CSI driver.
